Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

Get ready to groove with the full song of Aaj Ki Raat from Stree 2! Starring Tamannaah Bhatia and her electrifying dance moves, this catchy track is sung by Madhubanti Bagchi and Divya Kumar, with lyrics by Amitabh Bhattacharya and music by Sachin-Jigar. 

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Music Composer : Sachin - Jigar
Singers : Madhubanti Bagchi, Divya Kumar, Sachin -Jigar
Lyrics : Amitabh Bhattacharya 

All Music Produced Arranged & Designed By : Sachin-Jigar, Abhishek Singh (White Noise Collectives)
Music Production Head - Romil Ved 
Backings : Sumonto Mukherjee, Sahil Vishwakarma, Hrishikesh Gangan
Recording Engineer : Swar Mehta (White Noise Collective)
Mixed and Mastered by : Eric Pillai (FSOB Studio)
Assistant Mix Engineer : Michael Edwin Pillai
Choreographer :  Vijay Ganguly 
DOP: Jishnu Bhattacharjee

Jio Studios & Dinesh Vijan present Stree 2 

Starring: Shraddha Kapoor, Rajkummar Rao, Pankaj Tripathi, Abhishek Banerjee, and Aparshakti Khurana
Directed by: Amar Kaushik
Produced by: Dinesh Vijan
Produced by: Jyoti Deshpande
Written by: Niren Bhatt

snippet.title: Thozha - Back to Back comedy scene 2 | Karthi | Nagarjuna | Vivek | Tammanah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
The story revolves around Vikramadhitya (Nagarjuna) a quadriplegic billionaire, and Seenu, (Karthi) his ex-convict caretaker. Circumstances in their life teach them the value of relationships over money. 

Thozha is a 2016 movie . It was released in both Telugu and Tamil languages. Its name in Telugu is Oppri . The film is a remake of the French film The Intouchables . The film stars Karthik Sivakumar , Nagarsuna , Tamannaah , Prakasu Rasu , Vivek , Anushka , Seyashuda , Sireyya . The film is directed by Vamsi Baidipalli and produced by Prasad V Potluri.

snippet.title: Girls Hostel - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Minku hai bahut bada khiladi (played by Amit Bhadana) jo ek sath 3-3 girlfriends ko ghuma raha hai aur unke gifts aur paise kha raha hai. Lekin ek din Minku ki life mein aa jata hai bhuchal jab ek girlfriend uske samne rakh deti hai ek demand. Ye sabhi ladkiyan rehti hai ek hi Girls Hostel mein. Kaise bachayega Minku apni jaan? snippet.title: No Filter: Nia Sharma
snippet.description:
Hello Ji, Namaste Dooston Bharti TV Podcast Mein Aapka Fir Se Swagat Hai!

इस Episode में हम Nia Sharma के Diverse Life को Explore करते हैं, जिसमें उनकी Journey Daily Soaps से लेकर एक Fashion Icon तक का सफर शामिल है। Nia अपने Acting Career की शुरुआत, Evolving TV industry के बारे में अपने Views, और Fashion पर अपने Thoughts को Candid तरीके से Share करेंगी। वह अपने दो सबसे अच्छे Friends के साथ अपने Equation के बारे में भी बात करेंगी, जिन्हें वह प्यार से "Kids" कहती हैं। Marriage, Laughter Shows, और Sudesh Lehri के साथ काम करने के अपने Experience को भी Express करेंगी। हम उनकी Confidence, Male Attention को कैसे Handle करती हैं, और Brands के साथ उनके Negotiation के Experience पर भी चर्चा करेंगे। Nia अपने भाई, Vinay Sharma के साथ अपने Relation के बारे में भी बात करेंगी, और किस तरह के Projects पर वह आगे काम करना चाहती हैं इस पर भी चर्चा होगी। Nia यह भी बताएंगी कि क्या उन्हें Cooking आती है, और YouTube और 'Laughter Chef' Show पर अपनी राय भी देंगी। अंत में, हम उनके Anchoring और Hosting को लेकर उनके Perspective को भी Explore करेंगे!

Yeh Episode Nia Sharma Ke Life Aur Personality Ki Ek Khubsurat Jhalak Hai, Dekhte Rahiye Bharti TV!

#niasharma #bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya  #lolpodcast #podcast 

TIMESTAMPS:

(00:00) - Precap

(05:11) - Daily Soaps & Views on Fashion

(11:13) - Negotiation with Brands & People

(22:25) - Confidence, Male Attention & Marriage
(32:54) - Does Nia Know How to Cook?

(48:25) - Nia's Perception on Anchoring & Hosting
(51:39) - End Note

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: The Tri Folding Phone Durability Test! - someone has to try...
snippet.description:
The Triple Folding Smartphone From Huawei is here to be tested. Get a 4-week trial, free postage, and a digital scale at https://www.stamps.com/jerryrig. Thanks to Stamps.com for sponsoring the show! Folding smartphones and their soft flexible screens have been around for about 5 years now. Samsung has a few folding phones, Google has their Pixel fold. And now Huawei has the worlds first triple fold smartphone that is about the same size as an iPad. 
Today we are going to durability test the new tri fold smart phone called the Huawei Mate XT Ultimate Design and see how well it can hold up to every day life.

Lyrics-
Labhde firde maame tere pakke tikaane ve,
Laggu 26 ja 307 eh rabb hi jane ve,
Ho leke jamanat hafte vich aau bahar rakane ni,
Ho uthde behnde leader’an naal mere yaar rakane ni,
Ve laa laa naake sane gaddi tainu chakkan nu firde,
Ho darr na jattiye sade layi koi vadda masla nahi,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Jadd vi turde kafla naal tu leke turde ve,
Sheh ki jatt pendi na dasan di kade lod billo,
Dil dul ta ve lagda tera tutt da hona ni,
Kade kade vajjdiye pinde nu bas tod billo,
Taur Tappe to bina hor das ki ki kadh da o,
Kade kadai kande kade kadai tasla’an ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Darda vakil ve aulakha tera case koi fadd da nahi,
Saddi aakh kadhdiye kalli jane kaam koi khad da nahi,
Oh jadd tak ghar ni mud da ve dil jeha dar da rehnda ae,
Tere te hi marda aaukha saukha marda nahi,
Triple 0 1 LC vich kon ya hunda ve,
Jay virk jahe pakke yaar te nale pakkiya rafla ni,
Ve Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Tainu firde chakkan nu pale par tu thalle ni lagda,
Tahi ta tere aale jatt de utte lagde ni,
Ve dino dini tera tam jham jeha vadh da janda ae,
Mehar babe di sir te balliye tahio dabde nahi,
Vairi sadde ne naale tere te aakh ji rakde ne,
Hundiya ni tavi karde ne tere jatt diya nakla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni…

snippet.title: Sonu ने Start किया Chocolate का Business | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Chocolate Story
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Bhide informs everyone that the order has been cancelled, everyone tries to help him sell all the boxes of chocolates but fail to sell even a single box, just then Sonu comes home and informs everyone that someone has offered to buy all the boxes and he is coming to the society in the evening. Who is this secret angel?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2024 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah 

Click here to watch episodes from TMKOC: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLn5vww_8o5KtB8mEbckPmk4F9mKzG1qUm

snippet.title: Rattrap Class 12 In English | Summary/Questions And Answers/One Shot | Chapter 4 | Rattrap Movie
snippet.description:
Rattrap Class 12 In English | Chapter 4 Summary, Analysis & Questions | Full One-Shot Video Explanation

Welcome to this in-depth one-shot video on "The Rattrap" from Class 12 English! In this video, we’ll walk you through every essential detail of Chapter 4, including the full summary, character analysis, important questions and answers, and a thorough look at the chapter’s underlying messages. This video provides a complete breakdown of *The Rattrap* in a movie-like narration, making it easy and enjoyable for you to understand and remember.

 What You’ll Learn in This Video:

1. Chapter Summary
   We’ll explore The Rattrap by Selma Lagerlöf, a powerful story about redemption, human compassion, and the transformative power of kindness. Set against the harsh winter landscape of Sweden, the tale revolves around a poor peddler who sells rattraps and finds himself caught in life’s metaphorical traps. As we unfold the story, you’ll gain insights into how the peddler’s life changes after a fateful encounter with the ironmaster’s daughter, Edla, who treats him with compassion. This summary captures each scene and emotion to help you visualize the story vividly.

2. Character Analysis
   Get to know the main characters: the rattrap seller, who’s plagued by bitterness and mistrust, and Edla, who embodies kindness and empathy. We’ll analyze how each character’s actions and choices contribute to the story’s meaning and learn how the ironmaster and other supporting characters play a role in shaping the peddler’s journey.

3. Themes and Symbolism
   This story has a deeper symbolic layer that reveals life’s trials and the moral traps we often encounter. We’ll dive into the themes of trust, transformation, and human connection, explaining how *The Rattrap* uses symbolism to convey that kindness can change even the hardest hearts. This analysis will provide you with a nuanced understanding of the themes, which is essential for exams and helps develop critical thinking.

4. Questions and Answers
   We’ll tackle the most frequently asked exam questions, including short-answer questions, long-answer questions, and value-based questions. Our answers are structured to score well in exams, covering key points with clear, concise explanations. We’ll go through examples to demonstrate how to frame answers effectively.

5. Chapter Analysis and Author's Message 
   The Rattrap teaches us about empathy and the value of giving people second chances. We’ll explore Selma Lagerlöf’s background and her inspiration for writing this story. Through this analysis, we’ll understand how the author conveys that life’s challenges can sometimes feel like traps, but compassion can offer a way out.

 🎥 Bonus: Visual Summary Like a Movie!
   To make the story even more engaging, this video includes visuals and storytelling techniques to help you feel as if you’re watching the story unfold like a movie. We break down scenes and provide visual aids to ensure that you grasp every important moment, theme, and lesson. It’s a perfect tool for last-minute revision, ensuring you have a full understanding of the chapter in just one video!

Whether you're preparing for exams or just want to gain a deeper understanding of this classic story, this video covers all aspects in one easy-to-follow format. Hit the subscribe button for more chapter summaries, exam tips, and study resources for Class 12 English!

snippet.title: Making Halloween Costume Vlog in Tamil | Sheep Costume for Kids
snippet.description:
In this video join as I make some Halloween costumes for Alandra and Alaric. This year, I decided to get creative and make matching sheep costumes, perfect for a fun family Halloween look. Simple, affordable materials, like cotton balls and a basic dress, can be easily transform them into cute, fluffy sheep outfits.
#halloweencostume #sheepcostume #steffivlogs

Gluing cotton balls onto the dress to give it that perfect wooly sheep appearance. These homemade costumes are not only budget-friendly but also a great DIY Halloween costume idea for parents who love crafting unique and personalized outfits for their children. I hope this week's vlog inspires you to make your own homemade sheep costumes and enjoy a fun-filled crafting session with your little ones! See you soon with more interesting videos.

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about

snippet.description:

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 07 Teaser - 24th October 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar

Cast:

Wahaj Ali as Bilal Abdullah 
Maya Ali as Sadaf
Usama Khan as Ammar
Hira Mani as Hamsha
Amar Khan as Dania
Saba Hameed as Farzana
Syed Mohammed Ahmed as Namdaar
Shahvir Kadwani as Zaviyaar

#SunnMeraDil

snippet.title: 2 Minecraft Speedrunners VS TITAN
snippet.description:
2 Minecraft Speedrunners VS TITAN. You asked for it. The return of Minecraft Manhunt, George & Dream VS a real life Titan

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

George: @GeorgeNotFound 

Merch: https://www.dream.shop

All video music is custom scored and produced by Dream & PmBata. 

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt 2: TITAN TAKEDOWN. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is a massive, near invincible TITAN, being controlled by a real life human projected into the game using our custom fusion technology, instead of multiple hunters. This is the toughest challenge I have faced yet. GeorgeNotFound and I are on a team of 2, and are trying to speedrun and beat the game.

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.21 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my anonymous friend tries everything he can to stop me. This is all custom coded by us. 

If this video somehow gets 1,000,000 likes we'll announce the date of the next episode early.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftManhunt #MinecraftManhunt2

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: #Video | Chocolatey Sadiya | चॉकलेटी सड़िया | Khesari Lal Yadav | Priyanka Singh | Rajaram | Sapna C
snippet.description:
तैयार हो जाईं  " चॉकलेटी सड़िया" के मस्तीभरा बीट्स पर झूमे खातिर ट्रेंडिंग स्टार खेसारी लाल यादव और सपना चौहान के साथ चॉकलेटी अंदाज़ में

Subscribe to our channel for more
 Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Title - Chocolatey Sadiya
Hindi - चॉकलेटी सड़िया
Film : Rajaram राजाराम
Singer - Khesari Lal Yadav & Priyanka Singh
Music Director- Krishna Bedardi
Composer:- Kundan Preet
Lyrics - Kundan Preet
Feat - Khesari Lal Yadav & Sapna Chauhan
Director: Parag Patil
Producer: Parag Patil, R.R. Prince
Choreographer: - Prasun Yadav

Film Credits:
Production: - Technician Film Factory 
Producers: - Parag Patil & R.R. Prince 
Director: - Parag Patil

Lyrics:-

मुखड़ा 
फीमेल : का देखत बड़ा ये राजा जी बोला 
बाड़ा छीपावाले का भेद दिल के खोला
फीमेल :  का देखत बड़ा ये राजा जी बोला 
बाड़ा छीपावाले का भेद दिल के खोला

मेल : एक त दूधिया गोराई, दूजा तिल करिया मे 
चॉकलेटवे जइसन लागेलु चॉकलेटी सड़िया मे 

कोरस :चॉकलेटवे जइसन लागेलु चॉकलेटी सड़िया मे 

अंतरा 
मेल : बिंदिया तोहार लागे आसमान के 
कोरस :- जाने ऐ गोरी 
मेल :- बसें हमार तोहरे नाथूनिया मे 
कोरस :- पारने ऐ गोरी 
फीमेल : एतना बखान करके जान लेबा का ऐ राजा 
निहिया के सजल कुल दुकान लेबा का ऐ राजा 
मेल : मन करें एकदम रखले रही अकवारिया मे 
चॉकलेटवे जइसन लागेलु चॉकलेटी सड़िया मे 
कोरस :- चॉकलेटवे जइसन लागेलु चॉकलेटी सड़िया मे 

अंतरा २
मेल :- हीरा जइसन देह दूज कमशीन 
कोरस :- उमरिया ऐ गोरी 
मेल :-डाहे दूजे बज्जर तोर पतली 
कोरस :- कमरिया ऐ गोरी 
फीमेल :-एतना घूमवा जनी बतावा दिल के बतिया हो 
पोरे पोरे जानिले तोहार हम अदतिया हो 
मेल :- तोहार नियन ना फूल खिलाल कौनो फूलवारिया मे

snippet.title: चूड़ी से बनाये इस दिवाली की सबसे सरल रंगोली | Most Beautiful Diwali Rangoli | Deepawali Rangoli 2024
snippet.description:
Get ready to dazzle your friends and family with this stunning Diwali rangoli design made using a simple bangle trick! 
In this video, we'll show you a creative and easy way to create a beautiful Diwali rangoli using just a few bangles and some rangoli powder. 
This bangle trick rangoli is perfect for Diwali decorations and can be made in just a few minutes. 
So, watch till the end to learn this amazing Diwali rangoli design and make your Diwali celebrations even more special.
.
Happy Diwali To All 🪔
Rangoli By Radhika Saini
.
